  "page": 153,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0002",
      "text": " 134",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0003",
      "text": "6.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        109.88,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0004",
      "text": "Fabric Login",
      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        57.65,
        179.87,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0005",
      "text": "6.2.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        118.22,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0006",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        82.97,
        186.53,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0007",
      "text": "Login with the Fabric is required for all Nx_Ports, regardless of the class supported.  Communication",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.89,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0008",
      "text": "with other Nx_Ports shall not be attempted until the Fabric Login procedure is complete.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        483.79,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0009",
      "text": "Fabric Login accomplishes the following functions:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        318.19,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0010",
      "text": "a) It determines the presence or absence of a Fabric.",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        166.96,
        345.71,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0011",
      "text": "b) If a Fabric is present, it provides the Nx_Port with the specific set of operating characteristics",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        190.96,
        540.03,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0012",
      "text": "associated with the entire Fabric, F_Port_Name and Fabric_Name.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        202.96,
        418.52,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0013",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        226.96,
        114.34,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0014",
      "text": "If a Fabric is present, it provides the Fabric with the specific set of operating characteristics,",
      "bbox": [
        122.36,
        226.96,
        540.01,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0015",
      "text": "N_Port_Name and Node_Name of the Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        238.96,
        330.63,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0016",
      "text": "d) If a Fabric is present, the Fabric shall optionally assign or shall confirm the N_Port_ID of the",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        262.96,
        540.02,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0017",
      "text": "Nx_Port that initiated the Login.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        274.96,
        261.9,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0018",
      "text": "e) If a Fabric is present, it initializes the buffer-to-buffer Credit.",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        298.96,
        384.51,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0019",
      "text": "f)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        322.96,
        112.14,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0020",
      "text": "If the Nx_Port and the Fabric support Authentication, it enables the subsequent Nx_Port to",
      "bbox": [
        122.38,
        322.96,
        540.02,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0021",
      "text": "Fabric Authentication (see FC-SP).",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        334.96,
        277.26,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0022",
      "text": "g) If the N_Port and the Fabric support Virtual Fabrics, it enables the subsequent negotiation of",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        358.96,
        540.04,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0023",
      "text": "Virtual Fabrics parameters (see 8.2).",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        370.96,
        284.54,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0024",
      "text": "6.2.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        118.22,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0025",
      "text": "Explicit Fabric Login",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        394.96,
        226.55,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0026",
      "text": "6.2.2.1  Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        190.41,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0027",
      "text": "The explicit Fabric Login procedure shall require an Nx_Port to transmit a Fabric Login (FLOGI) Link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        539.97,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0028",
      "text": "Service ELS (see 4.2.7). ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        207.05,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0029",
      "text": "Explicit Fabric Login replaces previous Service Parameters. The Login procedure shall follow the Ex-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        540.0,
        490.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0030",
      "text": "change and Sequence management rules, the buffer-to-buffer flow control rules, and the end-to-end",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        540.11,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0031",
      "text": "flow control rules as specified in FC-FS-2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        280.89,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0032",
      "text": "6.2.2.2  Explicit Fabric Login Request",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        272.62,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0033",
      "text": "The Nx_Port shall transmit the FLOGI in a new Exchange.  The Payload of FLOGI contains the Ser-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        540.07,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0034",
      "text": "vice Parameters of the Nx_Port, a 64-bit N_Port_Name of the Nx_Port, and a 64-bit Node_Name.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        539.92,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0035",
      "text": "The Service Parameters are as specified for F_Port Login in 6.6.  The applicability of the Service Pa-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        539.96,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0036",
      "text": "rameters to Fabric Login are given in tables 150 and 155.  The Nx_Port shall assign an OX_ID and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        539.85,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0037",
      "text": "set the D_ID to the well-known F_Port address (i.e., FFFFFEh). ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        379.25,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0038",
      "text": "If the Nx_Port is unidentified, an Nx_Port shall set the S_ID in the FLOGI to 000000h or 0000h || YY.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        540.09,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0039",
      "text": "If the Nx_Port sets the S_ID to 000000h, the Nx_Port is requesting the Fabric assign all 24 bits of the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.02,
        539.98,
        646.13
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0040",
      "text": "N_Port_ID.  If the Nx_Port sets the S_ID to 0000h || YY, the Nx_Port is requesting the Fabric assign",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        539.92,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0041",
      "text": "the upper 16 bits, bits 23 to 8, and validate the lower 8 bits, bits 7 to 0, of the N_Port_ID.  An example",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        539.8,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p153_s0042",
      "text": "of the use of S_ID of 0000h || YY is FC-AL-2.  The lower 8 bits of the N_Port_ID are the AL_PA.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        518.94,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}